docs {
  # Create Product
  
  Creates a new product.
  
  **Required Fields:**
  - name: Product name
  - sku: Stock keeping unit (unique within organization)
  - category: Category
  - price: Selling price
  - stock_quantity: Stock quantity
  - unit: Unit (pcs, kg, liter, etc.)
}
